  <%- include('partials/header') %>

<!-- Welcome Section -->
<section class="welcome">
  <div class="container">
      <div class="text-content">
          <p class="subheading">Experience the Dorothy Care Difference</p>
          <h1 class="main-heading">Compassionate In-Home Care</h1>
          <p class="description">
              Providing personalized, high-quality care tailored to your loved one's unique needs.  
              Our dedicated team ensures comfort, dignity, and independence every step of the way.
          </p>
          <a href="/book" class="book-now">Schedule a Consultation</a>
      </div>
      <div class="image-content">
          <img src="images/founder1.jpg" alt="Caring caregiver assisting an elderly woman">
      </div>
  </div>
</section>

  <!-- Who We Are Section -->
  <section class="section who-we-are">
    <h2>Who We Are</h2>
    <p id="short-description">
      At <strong>Dorothy Care</strong>, we are a dedicated and compassionate care agency committed to delivering personalized, high-quality care services. With a focus on families and individuals, our mission is to provide care that is not only professional but also empathetic, ensuring that every client receives the attention and respect they deserve.
    </p>

    <!-- Full Description -->
    <p id="full-description" style="display: none;">
      Our team of experienced caregivers works tirelessly to create customized care plans that address the unique needs of each individual, offering tailored solutions to improve quality of life. We understand that the needs of our clients may vary, and our approach is built on flexibility, trust, and unwavering commitment to the well-being of those we serve.
      <br><br>
      At the heart of Dorothy Care is a deep sense of responsibility and compassion, as we believe that every person deserves to be treated with dignity and respect. Our caregivers are highly trained and share a common goal: to provide reliable, nurturing, and professional support to individuals in the comfort of their own homes.
      <br><br>
      Dorothy Care stands as a trusted partner in providing peace of mind to families, empowering individuals with the support they need to live comfortably and confidently. We strive to enrich lives through personalized, empathetic care that fosters a sense of security and well-being.
    </p>

    <!-- Read More / Less Link -->
    <a href="javascript:void(0)" id="read-more" onclick="toggleReadMore()">Read More</a>
  </section>

